title: E210 Dolan Twins Squash The Beef With Logan Paul - IMPAULSIVE EP. 210
itunes:title: Dolan Twins Squash The Beef With Logan Paul - IMPAULSIVE EP. 210
description:
In today’s episode, we find out how often the vegan Twins poop, if they‘ve ever shared a girlfriend, why they applied for Australian citizenship, & how they became arsonists at 11 years old. In addition, Logan & Grayson squash their beef (sort of) and the brothers discuss the passing of their father and how it’s affected their growth both personally and publicly.
